{"tid":1940623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國家衛生總監批評年輕人漠視指引 警告疫情或惡化","createTime":"2020-03-24T01:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T02:33:31.000Z","uid":80516,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21da8a17ddc5c22954c5adac74280a92a74d0aec","tid":1940623,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"美國至今超過3萬人確診新型肺炎，400多人死亡，國家衛生總監亞當斯警告，疫情會進一步惡化。<br />\n<br />\n亞當斯接受傳媒訪問時說，<span style=\"color: red;\">不少國民，特別是年輕人，漠視政府指引，無留在家中，過去周末湧去加州的海灘及首都華盛頓欣賞櫻花</span>。亞當斯認為，年輕人必須明白他們亦會受感染，導致可能入院，甚至致命，又說大家都需要假定自己是帶菌者，明白自己可以將病毒傳給其他人，亦可能被傳染。<br />\n<br />\n亞當斯又認為，目前毋須要求總統特朗普動用戰爭防衛生產特權法，迫令一些生產商加速生產一些急需的醫療裝備，因為生產商已經自行加工生產，重申解決問題的最佳方法，仍然是防止國民受感染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516384-20200324.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516384-20200324.htm&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1hV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=019f4145\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516384-20200324.htm&h=81b02aef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516384-20200324.htm</a>"},{"pid":"762d01837503a1253650ddc12d8d37bcf14cfc43","tid":1940623,"uid":30788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:48:14.000Z","msg":"cdc 指引話無需口罩wo"},{"pid":"78f97a1debd818b35db559f16519feeb8e7d825a","tid":1940623,"uid":45376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:52:25.000Z","msg":"just a flu"},{"pid":"7c31b43872929e4a98ba7f02107b371197016e5b","tid":1940623,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f97a1debd818b35db559f16519feeb8e7d825a","tid":1940623,"uid":45376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:52:25.000Z","msg":"just a flu"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"Think about it"},{"pid":"c064802afb2eeceaaac712547032f054520afb63","